Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい風のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描くよ　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:27.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さなことで揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:34.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱い自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣きたいときだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:45.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしだけにできることがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:54.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめないよ　君を守り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:02:00.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないスピードで想いがあふれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:06.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりも輝いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星がみえない日も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光はある　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じること…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い、　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:26.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの空で逢えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================opcn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:18.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}炫目的風中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描繪你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:27.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}變得坦率的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因小事而動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:34.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軟弱的自己令我懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仰頭忍淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:45.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必定有唯有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:54.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不言棄 一直守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:02:00.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思念正以停不下的速度膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:06.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願比任何人都耀目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使夜空沒有繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亦會有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往未來的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:26.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能在那片天空相逢
