Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2\blur4\pos(405,035)\fs26\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}Blue Days/Red Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說是真的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個學園都在討論這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個月的各學年競技賽拿了冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就能跟織斑交往了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏也知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看啊 當事人好像不太清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎只是在女生之間定下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回自己班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦 我也得坐回自己座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要是我拿了冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 就跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事為什麼會變成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個月的各學年競技賽拿了冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就能跟織斑交往了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種謠言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了冠軍能跟一夏交往的原本只應該是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我拿冠軍就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿冠軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 這次跟那時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是小學四年級的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都認為我肯定能奪冠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻沒能參賽 最後不戰而敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪姐姐發表了IS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS那壓倒性的性能 人們害怕會將它用作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一家 在「重要人物保護計劃」下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫不斷地搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跟父母分開住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也不知所蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被多次監視和叫去問話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心都倍感疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 唯有劍道 我堅持了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我和一夏唯一的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻變成個十分醜陋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀法是面反映自身的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 為了擊敗對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了消愁解悶而揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一種暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配稱作「強」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「強」所指的並不是那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不再迷失「強」的意義而勝出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 是戰勝自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為自己是第一個到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在各學年競技賽中拿冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要特訓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這機會 咱倆分個高下也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此分出誰更強更優雅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我比你強是不容置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說 狗越弱就吠得越凶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意要強調自己比別人強這點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就典型得不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原話 奉還!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國第三世代機「Schwarzer Regen」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(386,325)\fs16}（黑雨）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉·博迪薇希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然放冷槍 膽子真夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中國的甲龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有英國的Blue Tears嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還是看數據時比較強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 要打一場?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意離開德國 過來挨我抽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一個受虐狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是在土豆農場很流行這玩意?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐跟我們沒有共同語言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣來欺負她就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跟我一樣是第三世代的專用機擁有者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了人多就沒其他優點的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有只有陳舊是優點的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來真的很缺人才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人似乎希望被廢掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 兩人一塊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付為了隻無聊種馬而爭個不停的雌性動物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是聽見「請盡情毆打我吧」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連不在場的人都要侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我將你打到以後都不敢亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來就來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 今天也要特訓是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 距離競技賽已經沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說第三競技場有三個代表候補生在打模擬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凰和奧魯戈多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏拉·博迪薇希也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這台Schwarzer Regen的停止結界面前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擋下了龍咆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是AIC
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪 正是裝備了那個 才沒有躲開的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AIC? 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarzer Regen的第三世代兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Active Inertial Canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稱作慣性停止能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會被克得那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這種豆腐渣工程也配叫第三世代兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你停下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況下還用需時等待的空間壓兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼近還敢用導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真夠胡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過後再抱怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這下肯定給她造成傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分 那樣打 護盾能量撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果損傷積累
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS強制解除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆生命會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 拉烏拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝動兼動作單調
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典型的蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不配做我敵手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我和Schwarzer Regen面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是其中一塊雜碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 離遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 這些蝦兵蟹將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 白式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再用一次瞬時加速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看到難看的樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 兩個都還有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有專用機的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能站著傻看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一下 兩代之間的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對付小鬼才累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千冬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行模擬戰沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 連競技場的護罩都破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為老師 可不能默許
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥 到各學年競技賽再分勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然教官這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 迪諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對教師 要回答「是」蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒異議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 競技賽開始之前 禁止一切私鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也用不著你救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續打下去的話 我們就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都這麼胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡來?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 被心上人看到難看的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我才沒胡來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 你們怎麼會跟拉烏拉打起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被她侮辱了女性的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是不是關於一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼老是多了塊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒錯 就是多餘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆啊 都受傷了 還劇烈運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然還是痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻 別勉強自己嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻什麼傻啊 死蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏才是大傻瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死蠢死蠢死蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑\N迪諾亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼大家都跑來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本月舉行的各學年競技賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓模擬戰更具現實意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須兩人一組參加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 沒能找到拍檔的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將通過抽籤組成一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截止日期是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之啊 跟我拍檔吧 織斑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我拍檔吧 迪諾亞～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟夏爾魯拍檔 請找其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 比跟其他女生拍檔強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個男生在一起 美得像幅畫呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 跟我拍檔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是青梅竹馬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該跟我這個同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位的IS 受損程度已經超過C了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能允許你們參加競技賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定能好好打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前你們要專心修復機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然以後會成為重大缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了的女生 就會跟一夏交往是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點必須阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 冠軍就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆聽著 絕對要拿冠軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我們的份也要一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發自内心幫你們打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會努力回應兩位的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美麗的友情～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然有點晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 我做了什麼麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在保健室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了要跟我拍檔參加競技賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其他人拍檔 暴露你是女兒身就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 只有我在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己用男生口吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 來這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡為了不讓我暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我徹頭徹尾地學了男生口吻和動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計沒這麼快改回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果你在意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們單獨相處的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力表現得像個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得用男生口吻的夏爾魯也很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 這樣不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算你這麼說 我也會介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 都是男生 換個衣服還要你出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人會起疑心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們背對背換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拌到腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真看不出來 一夏原來喜歡霸王硬上弓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是好好說 我也不介意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就留在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次覺得自己被人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來這麼多大人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物色三年級的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看二年級比賽 確認一年下來的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各取所需 就來了很多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒會跟誰拍檔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是找不到拍檔的話 就要抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏似乎只在意跟博迪薇希的對戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博迪薇希目前恐怕是一年級裡最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手已經定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼組合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之戰 終於開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是別具特色的雙人組合戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在觀眾席上看 也超興奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不過 四個都是同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該支持誰好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持織斑那一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我給迪諾亞打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 兩個都是同一隊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 Find out my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂的鐘聲 即將響起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen2
